{"tid":2388771,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"首爾歌謠大賞丨定延歸隊 TWICE齊人奪本賞","createTime":"2021-01-31T11:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T15:35:59.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5d8ed8a48a8ba895364db173eface33d619f7e42","tid":2388771,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wMyuzgEloag6sN-r7xppxZHSt9Q=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DGNHA5PZFNEZBC4IT32B5MV5VA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwMyuzgEloag6sN-r7xppxZHSt9Q%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDGNHA5PZFNEZBC4IT32B5MV5VA.jpg&h=dd694d2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n定延（左一）孖TWICE成員於《第30屆首爾歌謠大賞》中奪本賞。<br />\n<br />\n韓國年度樂壇盛事《第30屆首爾歌謠大賞》今日在首爾蠶室室內體育館舉行，由於武漢肺炎疫情關係，今屆頒獎典禮以網上模式舉行，並由男團Super Junior成員金希澈孖申東燁和少女時代成員秀英擔任主持人。<br />\n<br />\n先拔頭籌得獎<br />\n韓劇《機智醫生生活》男星柳演錫擔任本賞的頒獎嘉賓，並由人氣女團TWICE先拔頭籌奪得本賞，成員上台領獎時表示：「過去的一年是令人鬱悶的一年，但希望今年能成為大家所期盼的幸福的一年，也請多多期待TWICE的活動。」台灣成員周子瑜就用韓文表示：「連續5年得到此獎，非常感謝，都是因為有fans的支持。」而早前因心理情況不穩而停工休養的定延，今日亦歸隊跟成員齊齊上台領獎，令fans非常驚喜。<br />\n<br />\nBTS奪本賞拍片謝fans<br />\n今年的新人獎就分別由YG事務所的新男團Treasure、SM事務所的新女團aespa及男團ENHYPEN奪得。之後由元祖男團神話成員金烔完頒發部份本賞，全球爆紅的人氣男團防彈少年團（BTS）亦獲得獎項，組合亦有拍片答謝fans。<br />\n<br />\n部份得獎名單<br />\n<br />\n本賞：TWICE、Seventeen、Stray Kids、姜丹尼爾、TXT、IZ*ONE、ATEEZ、防彈少年團（BTS）<br />\n<br />\n新人獎：Treasure、aespa、ENHYPEN<br />\n<br />\n最佳R&amp;B/Hip Hop：Jessi<br />\n<br />\n最佳Ballad：燦多<br />\n<br />\n最佳OST：趙正錫<br />\n<br />\n最佳Trot：任英雄<br />\n<br />\n最佳Band：LEENALCHI<br />\n<br />\n最佳Performance：(G)I-DLE、THE BOYZ<br />\n<br />\n年度發現獎：ITZY<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PHHbkzIQIIx0L06gK29efTHxpaw=/802x564/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O5JPJ4CKVZGN7GLPU7GDVL6X34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPHHbkzIQIIx0L06gK29efTHxpaw%3D%2F802x564%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO5JPJ4CKVZGN7GLPU7GDVL6X34.jpg&h=71fa6288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fuJ1Y2078HXBISieR_U81WcQ3GU=/802x516/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TCIKBMO6INBMFERHH277A66PEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfuJ1Y2078HXBISieR_U81WcQ3GU%3D%2F802x516%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTCIKBMO6INBMFERHH277A66PEM.jpg&h=43eaf38f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ec75742cd7938bd171978b29679f21866384b76","tid":2388771,"uid":33359,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:21:19.000Z","msg":"Twice又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea59f4247222093e6b2fccd9ecba48be8f9e72ac","tid":2388771,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:21:28.000Z","msg":"終於齊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a615cfdda4158ae9a5919d88facada5b6d4d24","tid":2388771,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:22:22.000Z","msg":"腎b..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b458f443e625b06b385002e9fe6331c8894d36","tid":2388771,"uid":173631,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:23:37.000Z","msg":"落b有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi